---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout locale="en" title="Welcome & Onboarding — ClosersMatch" description="You're signed up with ClosersMatch. Here's exactly what happens now: the onboarding portal, the welcome call, the conditions for kick-off, and what makes the partnership successful." noindex={true}>

  <!-- ================================================
       HERO
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="ob-hero">
    <div class="container container--narrow ob-hero__inner">
      <div class="ob-hero__icon" aria-hidden="true">🎉</div>
      <span class="label label--red">Welcome to ClosersMatch</span>
      <h1 class="ob-hero__title">Your start with professional deal closing.</h1>
      <p class="ob-hero__body">
        Great to have you on board as we get to work closing more deals together. This page gives you everything you need to start strong, clear, structured, and without surprises.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       WHAT WE DO / WHY THIS IS A GOOD MOVE
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section section--sm ob-intro">
    <div class="container ob-intro__grid">

      <div class="ob-intro__card">
        <h2 class="h3 ob-intro__title">What we'll do for you</h2>
        <p class="ob-intro__lead">From now on, we take care of:</p>
        <ul class="ob-check-list">
          <li><span class="ob-check-list__icon">✓</span>Professional closers who follow up your leads and close deals</li>
          <li><span class="ob-check-list__icon">✓</span>Full transparency into every conversation, follow-up, and result</li>
          <li><span class="ob-check-list__icon">✓</span>Contracts, invoicing, and legal protection through our platform</li>
          <li><span class="ob-check-list__icon">✓</span>Support with funnels, scripts, strategy, and optimizations where needed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ob-intro__card ob-intro__card--dark">
        <h2 class="h3 ob-intro__title">Why this is a good move</h2>
        <p class="ob-intro__lead">By signing up you automatically benefit from:</p>
        <ul class="ob-check-list">
          <li><span class="ob-check-list__icon">✓</span>A no cure, no pay partnership with professional closers</li>
          <li><span class="ob-check-list__icon">✓</span>Legal protection, escrow payments, and contract management</li>
          <li><span class="ob-check-list__icon">✓</span>Access to deal tracking in the ClosersMatch portal</li>
          <li><span class="ob-check-list__icon">✓</span>Replacement in case of dropout, plus active guidance from our team</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       STEPS CONTENT
  ================================================ -->
  <div class="container ob-layout">
    <aside class="ob-toc">
      <div class="ob-toc__card">
        <span class="ob-toc__label">On this page</span>
        <ul class="ob-toc__list">
          <li><a href="#step-1">Step 1 — Portal &amp; welcome call</a></li>
          <li><a href="#step-2">Step 2 — Ready for kick-off</a></li>
          <li><a href="#step-3">Step 3 — Start within 5 working days</a></li>
          <li><a href="#step-4">Step 4 — Cancelling or postponing</a></li>
          <li><a href="#step-5">Step 5 — Notice period &amp; agreements</a></li>
          <li><a href="#step-6">Step 6 — Access &amp; tools</a></li>
          <li><a href="#step-7">Step 7 — What determines your success</a></li>
          <li><a href="#availability">Availability &amp; communication</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="ob-content">

      <h2 id="step-1">Step 1 — Access to the Onboarding Portal &amp; welcome call</h2>
      <p>Once the partnership is confirmed, you'll receive:</p>

      <h3>🖥️ Onboarding Portal</h3>
      <p>A personal link to the ClosersMatch portal. Here you complete your onboarding by:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Filling in your company details, target audience, and offer.</li>
        <li>Uploading any documents or scripts.</li>
        <li>Setting up accounts and access for the closer.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>📞 Welcome call with our Sales Manager</h3>
      <p>Our sales manager will call you for a short kick-off check:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Reviewing your goals and expectations.</li>
        <li>Explaining the portal, way of working, and planning.</li>
        <li>Confirming everything is in place to start right away.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="step-2">Step 2 — What you need to have ready before kick-off</h2>
      <p>The kick-off isn't a casual introduction, it's the official starting point. That's why we only schedule it once the following is ready:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>📁 1. All basic information is provided</strong> — product, target audience, pricing structure, USPs, frequently asked questions, scripts (if available).</li>
        <li><strong>🔑 2. Access is arranged for the closer</strong> — CRM, mailbox, calendar, or lead file, depending on what's needed to get started right away.</li>
        <li><strong>📨 3. Leads are available directly in the portal</strong> — if you supply your own leads, they need to be in the ClosersMatch portal and up to date before kick-off. Without current leads the closer can't start, which immediately delays their compensation (and your results).</li>
        <li><strong>👤 4. Accounts are set up</strong> — ClosersMatch account, (if applicable) an email address for the closer or customer system, and access to tools such as CRM, Teams/Slack, VOIP, or calendar.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="ob-callout ob-callout--warning">
        <span class="ob-callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
        <div>
          <p class="ob-callout__title">Why this matters</p>
          <p>A closer only earns on closed deals. We reserve time, onboarding, and capacity, so once the kick-off happens, they need to be able to start immediately. If we schedule a kick-off and then have to wait days or weeks for leads or access:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>❌ The closer loses time and income.</li>
            <li>❌ You lose sales momentum and opportunities.</li>
            <li>✅ Under our terms, we may still start invoicing from day 5.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ob-callout ob-callout--summary">
        <span class="ob-callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">📌</span>
        <div>
          <p class="ob-callout__title">In short</p>
          <p>➡️ Kick-off = the start of the work, not preparation.<br />➡️ Preparation needs to be finished before the kick-off.<br />➡️ If it isn't, costs start, but results don't.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 id="step-3">Step 3 — After kick-off: start within 5 working days</h2>
      <p>After the kick-off, we start within 5 working days with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Following up on leads.</li>
        <li>Conversations and demos.</li>
        <li>Commercial activities to close deals.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="ob-callout ob-callout--warning">
        <span class="ob-callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
        <div>
          <p>Please note: if you don't provide access, leads, or a start within 5 working days after kick-off, ClosersMatch may pause or postpone the partnership, or the reserved closer capacity may be released.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 id="step-4">Step 4 — Cancelling or postponing? Here are the rules</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Before kick-off:</strong> free of charge.</li>
        <li><strong>After kick-off but before the first lead follow-up:</strong> a €1,000 onboarding fee (training &amp; reserved capacity).</li>
        <li><strong>After work has started:</strong> a 1-month notice period, with an average of 10 leads per week. If this isn't met, we'll charge for the estimated lost revenue.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="step-5">Step 5 — Notice period &amp; agreements</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Notice period: 1 month, regardless of results or deal status.</li>
        <li>Standard condition: keep supplying an average of 10 leads per week.</li>
        <li>Internal team members are welcome to meet the closer, but this may not delay the start.</li>
        <li>Kick-off is free, but not non-committal, we reserve time, training, and capacity.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="step-6">Step 6 — Access &amp; tools you'll receive</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Access via the ClosersMatch portal.</li>
        <li>Dashboard &amp; reporting.</li>
        <li>24/7 visibility into performance.</li>
        <li>Trained and screened closers.</li>
        <li>Recordings are made of all sales calls, we don't share them by default, but they're available if needed.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="step-7">Step 7 — What determines your success</h2>
      <p>To get the most out of our partnership:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>✔ Supply up-to-date, quality leads (or let us build the funnel for you).</li>
        <li>✔ Grant access to systems in a timely manner.</li>
        <li>✔ Respond quickly to the closer's questions.</li>
        <li>✔ Treat the partnership as an extension of your sales team, not a freelancer on the side.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="availability">Availability &amp; communication</h2>
      <p>We work with speed, structure, and transparency. To keep everything running smoothly, it's important that you stay reachable for questions, feedback, and appointments. During an active partnership, we ask you to respond to messages or requests within 24 hours. This prevents delays and ensures your leads or projects are followed up on immediately.</p>
      <p>All conduct and cooperation rules can be found in our House Rules: <a href="/house-rules">House Rules (EN)</a> · <a href="/nl/huisregels">Huisregels (NL)</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ================================================
       CLOSING
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="ty-closing">
    <div class="ty-closing__inner">
      <span class="ty-closing__icon" aria-hidden="true">🚀</span>
      <h2 class="ty-closing__title">Ready to get started?</h2>
      <p class="ty-closing__body">
        Once the steps above are complete, we'll schedule your kick-off and your closer will start within 5 working days. Have questions? We're here to help.<br />
        <a href="tel:+31634835912">+31 6 3483 5912</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="mailto:info@closersmatch.nl">info@closersmatch.nl</a>
      </p>
      <a href="/" class="ty-closing__back">← Back to the homepage</a>
      <p class="ty-closing__brand">ClosersMatch. <span>The Revenue Ecosystem.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ====================================================
     HERO
  ==================================================== */
  .ob-hero {
    padding: 140px 0 56px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ob-hero__inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ob-hero__icon {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .ob-hero__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin: 12px 0 20px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .ob-hero__body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ob-hero { padding: 110px 0 40px; }
  }

  /* ====================================================
     INTRO CARDS
  ==================================================== */
  .ob-intro__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ob-intro__card {
    background: var(--color-gray-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 32px 28px;
  }

  .ob-intro__card--dark {
    background: var(--color-black);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .ob-intro__title {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .ob-intro__card--dark .ob-intro__title {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .ob-intro__lead {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ob-intro__card--dark .ob-intro__lead {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  .ob-check-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ob-check-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #333;
  }

  .ob-intro__card--dark .ob-check-list li {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
  }

  .ob-check-list__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-red);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ob-intro__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ====================================================
     LAYOUT: TOC + CONTENT
  ==================================================== */
  .ob-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px minmax(0, 720px);
    gap: 56px;
    padding-top: 72px;
    padding-bottom: 96px;
    max-width: 1080px;
  }

  .ob-toc__card {
    position: sticky;
    top: 110px;
    background: var(--color-gray-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 24px 22px;
  }

  .ob-toc__label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .ob-toc__list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .ob-toc__list a {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.4;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .ob-toc__list a:hover { color: var(--color-red); }

  .ob-content {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #2a2a2a;
  }

  .ob-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 48px 0 16px;
    color: var(--color-black);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }

  .ob-content h2:first-of-type { margin-top: 8px; }

  .ob-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 24px 0 10px;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .ob-content p {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ob-content strong {
    color: var(--color-black);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ob-content ul {
    margin: 0 0 16px 22px;
  }

  .ob-content li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .ob-content a {
    color: var(--color-red);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  /* Callout boxes */
  .ob-callout {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .ob-callout--warning {
    background: rgba(221, 52, 46, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(221, 52, 46, 0.2);
  }

  .ob-callout--summary {
    background: var(--color-gray-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-border);
  }

  .ob-callout__icon {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .ob-callout__title {
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: 6px !important;
  }

  .ob-callout p:last-child,
  .ob-callout ul:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .ob-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .ob-toc__card {
      position: static;
    }
  }

  /* ====================================================
     CLOSING (matches thank-you pages)
  ==================================================== */
  .ty-closing {
    background: var(--color-black);
    padding: 100px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ty-closing__inner {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ty-closing__icon {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ty-closing__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ty-closing__body {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .ty-closing__body a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ty-closing__body a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .ty-closing__back {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .ty-closing__back:hover {
    border-color: #fff;
  }

  .ty-closing__brand {
    margin-top: 48px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .ty-closing__brand span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }
</style>
